	<h1 class="title">直男癌游戏《刺客信条》迎来了第一个跨性别角色</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/57300/small/57300.jpg?1427187252" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐舒畅 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-25 19:23:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15573/medium/15573.jpg?1443165046" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


